<%# GOAL (green) / MISS (red) outcome label for one penalty shootout kick.
    Each branch keeps its colour as a STATIC class literal so Tailwind reliably
    generates the rule — an arbitrary colour tucked inside an ERB ternary isn't
    always picked up by the content scanner. %>
<% if kick.was_scored %>
  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider shrink-0 text-[#1c5c3f]">Goal</span>
<% else %>
  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] sm:text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-wider shrink-0 text-[#b91c1c]">Miss</span>
<% end %>
